: 668}, {\"ngram\": \"the exercise\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"a success\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French legislation passed in 2023 permits the use of AI video surveillance for a trial period covering the Games to detect abnormal events or human behaviour at large-scale events.\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 718, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8251309150701409, \"rank\": 0.20750005985859915, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 771, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2223850069292373e-19, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"a trial period\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"abnormal events\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"human behaviour\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"large-scale events\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 897}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The technology could be pivotal to thwarting an attack like the bombing at the 1996 Olympics in Atlanta or the Nice truck attack in 2016, officials say.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.999999999699412, \"rank\": 2.9970914063010296e-10, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}, {\"begin\": 1011, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\", \"sc